Privacy Policy
This website does not download any personal information nor does it collect or use any personal data of any kind.
Paid game versions.
Games by John Gregory, including ‘War in Europe’ and ‘French and Indian war’ do not collect or use personal information or collect or use any personal data or any tracking of any kind.
Free-to-play game versions.
Then using the free-to-play game versions, these games will have 3rd party ads running. These ads can have tracking and will track you search history and data collection. they will use this information to target ads that will be of more interest to you.
My games run using Googles AdMod, below is their Privacy Usage details.
